# [MAILMAINT](../wg/mailmaint.html)

## Summary

The MAILMAINT Working Group met at IETF 126 in Vienna. The session covered updates on active working group documents, technical discussions on mail autoconfiguration, SMTPUTF8 email address syntax, personal data portability archives, unobtrusive end-to-end signatures, and updates to IMAP Object IDs.

